advanced.description:
{Precision - Advanced}

Increases the selected allied shooter's Attack by +6 for ranged attacks only.

Additionally, extends its full-damage shooting range by 1 hex, up to 11 hexes, and grants +1 Speed for spell duration.

expert.description:
{Precision - Expert}

Increases all allied shooters' Attack by +6 for ranged attacks only.

Additionally, extends their full-damage shooting range by 2 hexes, up to 12 hexes, and grants +1 Speed for spell duration.
